{
  "title": "Tangy Wood Fired Moroccan Chicken Tagine",
  "description": "A sour and juicy Moroccan dish featuring glace cherry, wood-fired-baked in an agave leaf vessel, with ayurvedic-rajasic-friendly ingredients. This meal prep recipe is perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
