  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the wood fired oven to 425 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, ginger, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken thighs to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Let the chicken marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Place the marinated chicken thighs in an agave leaf vessel.",
    "Add the glace cherry on top of the chicken.",
    "Bake the chicken in the preheated wood fired oven for 35 minutes.",
    "Let the chicken rest for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve the chicken hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
